Package: chleb-bible-search
Architecture: all
Depends: chleb-bible-search-core (= ${binary:Version}), chleb-bible-search-dict (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Chleb Bible Search - Bible Query Service (meta-package)
 This is a meta package that installs both the core bible search service, which provides the main
 functionality for searching within the Bible text and the dictionary data, which contains the necessary
 linguistic data for interpreting search queries.

