Package: chleb-bible-search-dict
Architecture: all
Depends: chleb-bible-search-core (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Chleb Bible Search - Core Dictionaries
 This package contains the dictionary data used by the Chleb Bible Search service.
 It includes linguistic data for interpreting search queries.
